version_description: Much more accurate than the other contributions and is suitable to play alongside recording.
Place a capo on the 3rd fret to make the chords easier to play. If you prefer barre chords, lose the capo and transpose up 3 steps.
It is an accurate version for beginners, so it has no barre chords or challenging chords to play
NOTE: Please note that the chords are a little different because i tried to make it easier for people who dislike bar chords, or for novices. But also note that is does sound close to the original.
